      "span_text": "The geometry of the deposition system is described elsewhere. [CITATION_1] Zr and Y metallic targets of one-inch diameter and 99.99% pure from ACI alloys, USA were used for the deposition of YSZ lms. (100) oriented Si wafers from Siltronix SAS, France, were diced to 1 Â 1 cm 2 and were used as substrates.",
